=== overview ===
**The Rule of Three**
Three of anything is a distress signal.
- 3 Fires.
- 3 Whistle blasts.
- 3 Flashes of light.
- 3 Gunshots.

**Rescue Chopper**:
- Stand with arms up (Y shape) = Yes/Help.
- One arm up = No/Okay.
- Never run towards it.

